{"word":"θήκη","slug":"θήκη","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>θήκη</b></el> <el>(θήκη, ἡ,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:τίθημι'><el>τίθημι</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>a case to put anything in, a box, chest</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>a place for corpses, a grave, tomb</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>a mode of burial</i>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}